> Bill Page wrote:
> 
> >
> >> C Y wrote:
> >> 
> >...(snip)...
> >> You might want to read 
> >> http://www.cs.berkeley.edu/~fateman/papers/openmathcrit.pdf
> >> to see some of his objections to OpenMath.
> >
